{"tid":667531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(同侵侵唱反調) FBI局長：嚴重擔憂「中興」這類企業","createTime":"2018-05-16T23:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T02:13:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c67f993ceffeb8efb32adc60dc5749af10fa16e","tid":667531,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:44:20.000Z","msg":"FBI之前一直俾Donald Trump狂屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.worldjournal.com/5571278/article-fbi%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E9%80%99%E9%A1%9E%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD/?ref=%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F5571278%2Farticle-fbi%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2593%2594%25E6%2586%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2588%25E9%2580%2599%25E9%25A1%259E%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%2F%3Fref%3D%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%2596%25A6%25E9%2596%25B1%25E8%25AE%2580&d=QZGlUmFjcFsXdRC5pcKbXy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5033e561\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.worldjournal.com/5571278/article-fbi%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E9%80%99%E9%A1%9E%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD/?ref=%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80</a></span><br />\n<br />\nFBI局長：嚴重擔憂中興這類企業<br />\n記者羅曉媛／華盛頓報導 2018年05月16日 18:52 <br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局(FBI)局長雷伊(Christopher Wray)16日在參院預算委員會表示，FBI「嚴重擔憂」(deeply concerned)像中國中興這類在美國通訊市場獲取權位(positions of power)的公司。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>雷伊16日在參院預算委員會就FBI在2019財年的預算作證，但聽證會最終變成圍繞中國間諜能力的討論會。<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部上月宣布在7年內禁止美國企業向中國的電信設備製造商中興通訊公司銷售零件。但川普總統近日來連發數條「救中興」的推特，其有意違背商務部「封殺令」之勢，在國會乃至美國社會招致反對和困惑。<br />\n<br />\n雷伊當日表示，他並不知道川普在發布「救中興」推特前，是否曾試圖諮詢FBI的意見。他指出，對於由和美國不同價值觀的外國政府支持(beholden)的任何企業，FBI繼續表示深度擔憂，也不希望這些企業在美國通訊市場獲得權位，因為會讓這些企業有能力去惡意修改或盜竊信息，並進行間諜活動。"},{"pid":"cfa89c12f11a7b2e402566345dc30a748e7d7606","tid":667531,"uid":57376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T23:57:31.000Z","msg":"全美反中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d1ec38669c1ada06aeef93f4d45ccb327e802f","tid":667531,"uid":95096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"美國反中之父trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同689一樣"},{"pid":"8d137d7cf86fae183c4aabc27752fdf49c35f2c6","tid":667531,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:19:10.000Z","msg":"Trump：刁！你睇！我被逼架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1c8037f043e677512184697d355fb04c750e84","tid":667531,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28d1ec38669c1ada06aeef93f4d45ccb327e802f","tid":667531,"uid":95096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"美國反中之父trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同689一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0aa2766790f1ed41f6bb742b7d4c664eb4f1050","tid":667531,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c8e72895936816dd1108cf1a574ab4b68f7fbd","tid":667531,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"萬一侵侵落台，反中勢力會唔會更肆無忌憚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9044721dfe9e10438007ba8dca5578e7e03ddc55","tid":667531,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7174b522fb03bfb3d9f223abfbdb23b149e2de2a","tid":667531,"uid":56321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"[突發] 有人在白宮聯署網站提出凍結香港政策法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/t/658941/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/t/658941/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署link：<a href=\"http://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-president-trump-freeze-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-president-trump-freeze-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act&d=QZGlUmFjcFsXdRC5pcKbXy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1b84f31a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-president-trump-freeze-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act</a><br />\n<br />\n因為Trump彈弓手想放生中興，襯而家中興件事係美國鬧大咗同爭議大咗<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有人send呢個聯署去美國參衆兩院議員電郵，同埋共和民主兩黨，再加右翼政黨黨員電郵？<br />\n<br />\n最好send埋去反Trump嘅media, e.g. CNN, 同埋每個Trump嘅twitter post 都reply呢個聯署，最好加埋原因，Trump個邊大把美國公民留言唔妥放生中國<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;"},{"pid":"d5546ea6d89504fb384f7b07211835adf6e31124","tid":667531,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca1c8037f043e677512184697d355fb04c750e84","tid":667531,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28d1ec38669c1ada06aeef93f4d45ccb327e802f","tid":667531,"uid":95096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"美國反中之父trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同689一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"dark knight"},{"pid":"9bd340719e125b7d841f4e4f5ecd491191ff4c96","tid":667531,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5546ea6d89504fb384f7b07211835adf6e31124","tid":66753